{"article_id":"8m7xb8esSwiA2RAE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After 10 long months of delay and recalcitrance , President Donald Trump has finally submitted his answers to some of special counsel Robert Mueller ' s questions on Russian interference with the 2016 election ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"according to the president ' s personal lawyers .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"We don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"whether these answers will be forthright ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"or whether the president will try to dodge the questions","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"asked ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"since the format doesn ' t allow for immediate follow-ups .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"( Last week , Trump told Fox News ' s Chris Wallace","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that he \" probably \" wouldn ' t voluntarily agree to answer further questions from Mueller","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"or do an in-person interview with the special counsel ' s team . )","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"But Trump submitting his answers is still a significant moment for the probe .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Unlike his many public statements , these statements to the special counsel are submitted at risk of legal penalties","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"for making false statements .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"And after investigators judged President Bill Clinton to have made false statements in a deposition and grand jury interview ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"congressional Republicans made those statements the basis for articles of impeachment against him .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Trump has spent hours","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"meeting with his lawyers about the questions over several sessions ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"per the Washington Post .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The morning after one meeting last week , he sent a series of tweets","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"calling the Mueller investigation \" a disgrace to our Nation \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that was trying to \" destroy people \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and \" ruin \" lives","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"- perhaps a sign","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"he was having trouble with his answers .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"It is possible that Trump has nothing serious to hide .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Maybe his many months","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"of refusing to agree to answer these questions","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"are solely because he ' s being cautious","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"because he fears","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"a \" perjury trap \" or a \" witch hunt \" will ensnare him","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"even though he ' s done nothing wrong .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Maybe the fact","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that he ' s only answering these","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"now that he ' s installed a new acting attorney general","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he views as more loyal","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"is also just a coincidence .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"if there is more to the story of what happened in 2016","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"than Trump has so far admitted ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"then the president has likely been struggling with some difficult choices behind the scenes .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Such as :","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Does he fess up to politically damaging and perhaps legally perilous conduct ?","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Or does he continue to try to conceal , or lie about , what happened","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"- even in statements","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"made under penalty of perjury ?","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" Will Mueller interview Trump \" has become","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" Will Trump deign to answer a very limited set of Mueller ' s questions \"","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"All the way back in January , Mueller ' s team first requested to question Trump as part of their investigation .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"The stakes were high .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Trump ' s statements about many topics have often been ... factually challenged .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"But they are generally made to the press and the public , and not to federal law enforcement officers .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Should Trump make false statements to Mueller ' s team ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"there could be legal consequences for him","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"( potential impeachment","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"while he ' s in office ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"or even criminal charges","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"after he leaves it ) .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"In March , Mueller ' s team told Trump ' s lawyers about various topics","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"they hoped to ask Trump about in person .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Trump ' s lawyers used this information","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"to assemble a list of more than 40 likely questions ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"which the New York Times obtained earlier this year .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Many of these questions related to obstruction of justice","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"( connected to Trump ' s firing of FBI Director James Comey and pressure on Attorney General Jeff Sessions ) ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"but many others related directly to Russian interference .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Trump ' s team decided","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"they did not want to have him answer these questions .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"They offered various shifting excuses","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"for not agreeing to do the interview","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"( while dubiously claiming","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Trump himself still wanted to do it ) .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"The most common justifications for refusal were that they feared a \" perjury trap , \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that Trump had a tendency","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"to make off-the-cuff misstatements ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and that they had constitutional executive power concerns about the obstruction of justice questions .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"All this time , the threat","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"of Mueller subpoenaing Trump","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"was hanging over everything .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"( Mueller himself explicitly mentioned that possibility to Trump ' s team ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"per the Post . )","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"This is one likely reason","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Trump didn ' t just refuse to answer questions outright .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Many legal experts believed","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"that Trump would likely lose a battle over a subpoena in court ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"were one to occur .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"But that battle would take some time","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"and hold up the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Eventually , a compromise was struck .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"For at least an initial set of questions , Mueller ' s team agreed","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"that Trump could answer in written form , rather than orally","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"- minimizing the chances for an off-the-cuff misstatement .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"And he scaled back these initial questions","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"to focus on the topic of collusion with Russia , not obstruction .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Mueller sent Trump those questions by mid-October .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"According to the Washington Post ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"there are about two dozen questions","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that focus on five topics .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"More than a month has passed since then .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"And finally , Trump sat down with his lawyers over several lengthy meetings last week","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"to craft his answers .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Bill Clinton thought","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"he could get away with lying about Monica Lewinsky","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"About 20 years ago , President Bill Clinton was in a similar position .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"In a January 1998 deposition for Paula Jones ' s sexual harassment lawsuit against him , Clinton was quizzed about his interactions with several women ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"including former White House intern and then employee Monica Lewinsky .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"At the time , Clinton ' s affair with Lewinsky wasn ' t publicly known .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"If Clinton admitted to it ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"he ' d cause a major scandal","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"and suffer political embarrassment .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"if he lied about it ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"he might get away with it .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"What evidence could there be , anyway ?","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"So Clinton proceeded to lie repeatedly ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"ludicrously claiming","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that he didn ' t think","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"he and Lewinsky had ever been alone in the Oval Office together ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"if they had been together ,","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"\" nothing remarkable \" would have happened ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"and that he had \" never had sexual relations with Monica Lewinsky . \"","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"News of the affair broke days after the deposition .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Clinton continued to deny it publicly ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"but independent counsel Ken Starr ' s prosecutors amassed evidence","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"including Lewinsky ' s taped conversations , a blue dress","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"stained with Clinton ' s semen , and ( eventually ) Lewinsky ' s cooperation .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"So","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"when Clinton agreed to testify to Starr ' s grand jury ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"he finally admitted","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"when he was \" alone with Ms. Lewinsky on certain occasions , \"","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"he had \" inappropriate , intimate contact \" with her .","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"Still , Starr argued","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"that Clinton lied three more times in the grand jury testimony , about the details and timeline of the affair .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"( In the end , Clinton did \" get away with it \" in a sense after all ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"since he was impeached","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"but not convicted ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"and he remained in office . )","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"So hypothetically ,","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"if someone is trying to get away with lying under oath","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"rather than make damaging admissions ,","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"they are likely thinking about several questions .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"What do prosecutors suspect ?","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"What do they know for sure ?","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"What are they likely to find out eventually ?","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"What will they have witnesses","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"willing to testify about ?","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"What can they prove with evidence ?","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"Depending on the answers of these questions ,","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"it may be possible to get away with lies","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"- or to get busted .","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"Did Trump have an easy time","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"answering the questions ?","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"Accounts differ .","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"The Washington Post reported","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"that Trump and his lawyers had a four-hour meeting about the questions last Monday , and a 90-minute meeting Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"The morning after that second meeting , Trump sent a series of angry tweets about the Mueller investigation .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"We don ' t know","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"what ' s been going on behind the scenes ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"but he certainly seemed agitated about the probe :","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"The inner workings of the Mueller investigation are a total mess .","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"They have found no collusion","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"and have gone absolutely nuts .","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"They are screaming","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"and shouting at people ,","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"horribly threatening them","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"to come up with the answers","depth":17},{"id":168,"text":"they want .","depth":17},{"id":169,"text":"They are a disgrace to our Nation","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"and don ' t ...","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":16},{"id":172,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"November 15 , 2018","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"....","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"care how many lives the ruin .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"These are Angry People ,","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"including the highly conflicted Bob Mueller ,","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"who worked for Obama for 8 years .","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"They won ' t even look at all of the bad acts and crimes on the other side .","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"A TOTAL WITCH HUNT LIKE NO OTHER IN AMERICAN HISTORY !","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"November 15 , 2018","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"Universities will someday study what highly conflicted","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"( and NOT Senate approved )","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"Bob Mueller and his gang of Democrat thugs have done","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"to destroy people .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"Why is he protecting Crooked Hillary , Comey , McCabe , Lisa Page & her lover , Peter S , and all of his friends on the other side ?","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"November 15 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"Naturally , Trump then insisted to Chris Wallace","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"that answering the questions wasn ' t \" a big deal \"","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"and was \" very simple , \"","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"because \" I did nothing wrong. \"","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"He did not explain","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"why it ' s taken him so long to send the answers .","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"His lawyer Rudy Giuliani didn ' t make it sound so simple .","depth":6},{"id":199,"text":"Around the same time , he told the Post","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"that there were some of Mueller ' s questions","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"that \" create more issues for us legally than others , \"","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"that some were \" unnecessary , \"","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"that some were \" possible traps , \"","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"and that he might \" consider some as irrelevant . \"","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"Meanwhile , an update on Paul Manafort is coming by Monday","depth":4},{"id":206,"text":"In the midst of all this , Mueller ' s team submitted an interesting joint court filing with lawyers for Paul Manafort .","depth":7},{"id":207,"text":"The former Trump campaign chair agreed to cooperate with Mueller ' s investigation as part of a plea deal in September .","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"Since then , he ' s left jail","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"to travel to the special counsel ' s office at least nine times ,","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"per CNN .","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"However , ABC News had a recent report","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"claiming","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"that the cooperation isn ' t going well","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"- that there is \" frustration","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"over whether Manafort is fully providing the information","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"he agreed to offer . \"","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"Now , the new Manafort filing asks for just a 10-day extension","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"in submitting an update about his case .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"\" The parties believe","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"a brief extension of the status report date , until November 26 , 2018 , will allow them to provide the Court with a report","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"that will be of greater assistance in the Court ' s management of this matter , \"","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"they write .","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"This is an unusually short extension for an update like this .","depth":8},{"id":224,"text":"It suggests","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"that something will happen quite soon","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"- by Monday -","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"that will clarify Manafort ' s case .","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"( Don ' t expect big new details , necessarily ,","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"but we may get a clearer sense","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"of how his cooperation has gone and whether he ' s ready for sentencing . )","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"Marcy Wheeler suggests several possible reasons for the short extension ,","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"with one of them being that Trump was expected to submit his answers to Mueller by then .","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"Perhaps Manafort ' s cooperation relates to those answers ,","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"and Mueller is waiting to have the answers in hand","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"before revealing how cooperative or uncooperative Manafort is being .","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"Trump also told Wallace","depth":8},{"id":237,"text":"that he \" probably \" won ' t agree to any further questioning from Mueller ' s team -","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"meaning that he likely wouldn ' t answer questions","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"about whether he obstructed justice while in office ,","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"and likely wouldn ' t agree to be interviewed in person .","depth":10},{"id":241,"text":"While many have long believed","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"that Trump would never end up agreeing to an in-person interview with Mueller ,","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"his public admission of this is significant","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"- and notably comes","depth":12},{"id":245,"text":"right after he ' s ousted Jeff Sessions","depth":13},{"id":246,"text":"and gone around DOJ ' s line of succession","depth":14},{"id":247,"text":"to install a loyalist , Matt Whitaker , as acting attorney general .","depth":14},{"id":248,"text":"Whitaker now oversees the special counsel investigation .","depth":11},{"id":249,"text":"Whether he yet knows the inner workings of the probe ,","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"and if so ,","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"whether he ' s told Trump anything about them","depth":14},{"id":252,"text":"or interfered in any way ,","depth":14},{"id":253,"text":"remains mysterious .","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":10},{"id":255,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"recently met with Whitaker ,","depth":9},{"id":257,"text":"and claimed","depth":9},{"id":258,"text":"that Whitaker said","depth":10},{"id":259,"text":"he ' s following \" regular order \" with regards to the investigation .","depth":10},{"id":260,"text":"But Trump may believe","depth":9},{"id":261,"text":"Whitaker ' s appointment removes or lessens the threat of a Mueller subpoena","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"that ' s been hanging over him all these months .","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"\" White House aides and other people close to Mr. Trump anticipate","depth":11},{"id":264,"text":"that Mr. Whitaker will rein in any report","depth":13},{"id":265,"text":"summarizing Mr. Mueller ' s investigation","depth":13},{"id":266,"text":"and will not allow the president to be subpoenaed , \"","depth":12},{"id":267,"text":"the New York Times reported shortly after Whitaker ' s appointment .","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"Around the same time , \" two people close to Whitaker \" told the Washington Post","depth":10},{"id":269,"text":"that \" he is deeply skeptical of any effort","depth":11},{"id":270,"text":"to force the president ' s testimony through a subpoena . \"","depth":11},{"id":271,"text":"And now , Trump seems to believe","depth":5},{"id":272,"text":"he ' s solved his problem .","depth":5},{"id":273,"text":"Asked about answering more Mueller questions ,","depth":6},{"id":274,"text":"he told Wallace ,","depth":7},{"id":275,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":276,"text":"we ' ve wasted enough time on this witch hunt","depth":9},{"id":277,"text":"and the answer is probably , we ' re finished . \"","depth":8},{"id":278,"text":"\" We gave very , very complete answers to a lot of questions","depth":9},{"id":279,"text":"that I shouldn ' t have even been asked","depth":9},{"id":280,"text":"and I think","depth":9},{"id":281,"text":"that should solve the problem , \"","depth":9},{"id":282,"text":"he continued .","depth":7},{"id":283,"text":"\" I hope","depth":8},{"id":284,"text":"it solves the problem ,","depth":8},{"id":285,"text":"if it doesn ' t ,","depth":9},{"id":286,"text":"you know ,","depth":10},{"id":287,"text":"I ' ll be told","depth":11},{"id":288,"text":"and we ' ll make a decision at that time .","depth":11},{"id":289,"text":"But probably this is the end . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":579,"left":390,"right":578,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":390,"left":347,"right":389,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":347,"left":313,"right":346,"rel